OL,3,CMan accused of murder after pub
OL,4,Clandlord assaulted appears in court
OL,6,FA man accused of murder after another
OL,7,Fman died following an assault outside
OL,8,Fa bar has appeared in court.
OL,10,FBilly Allison, 36, appeared at
OL,11,FStafford Crown Court after being
OL,12,Fcharged with murder and Section 18
OL,13,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent in
OL,14,Fconnection with an incident in
OL,15,FLichfield on May 24.
OL,17,FStaffordshire Police said officers
OL,18,Fwere called to the Ricco and Loren bar
OL,19,Fon Market Street at 11.25pm following
OL,20,Freports two men had been punched.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
