OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780045515
OL,3,CMan accused of murder after pub
OL,4,Clandlord assaulted appears in court
OL,6,FOne of the men sustained serious
OL,7,Finjuries and died in hospital on
OL,8,FTuesday.
OL,10,FHe has been named locally as pub
OL,11,Flandlord Matthew O'Gara who was a
OL,12,Fbusiness partner at The Plough Inn in
OL,13,Fnearby Huddlesford.
OL,15,FThe second victim in the assault was
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital but has since been
OL,17,Fdischarged.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
