PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780045515
OL,3,CMan accused of murder after pub
OL,4,Clandlord assaulted appears in court
OL,6,FWearing a blue long-sleeved top,
OL,7,FAllison, of Solihull, appeared before
OL,8,FJudge Avik Mukherjee for an eight-
OL,9,Fminute hearing on Thursday and spoke
OL,10,Fonly to confirm his name when asked by
OL,11,Fthe court clerk.
OL,13,FThe court heard a date for trial,
OL,14,Fexpected to last two weeks, was set
OL,15,Ffor October 26.
OL,17,FThe judge told the defendant, who
OL,18,Fstood with his hands clasped in front
OL,19,Fof him, he would next appear in court
OL,20,Fin September and would be remanded
OL,21,Finto custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
