PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1780045515
OL,3,CMan accused of murder after pub
OL,4,Clandlord assaulted appears in court
OL,6,FHe said: "Billy Allison, will you
OL,7,Fstand please.
OL,9,F"Your next hearing is the first of
OL,10,FSeptember and you will be produced to
OL,11,Fcourt for that hearing."
OL,13,FOf his trial, the judge said: "You
OL,14,Fhave an obligation to come.
OL,16,F"You are expected to be here every day
OL,17,Ffor your trial."
OL,19,FAllison nodded and was taken back down
OL,20,Fto the cells by a custody officer
OL,21,Ffollowing the hearing.
